get_available_sizes[source]

get_available_sizes(dirpath:str, prefix:str, input_names:], output_names:])->]]

Get all available json weight hidden sizes given filename parameters

Note: this function does NOT return the input size and the output size of the neural network. ONLY the hidden sizes are reported. The input and output sizes can easily be derived from input_names (after preprocessing) and output_names.
